It has a large playing field and netball court in the playground. The pupils come from Benington, Butterwick, Freiston and Leverton. In between lessons we have our playtimes.
Many of us arrive at{8.30 am}but some come on a later bus or they walk. We go in at{9.00 am}.We have a service at {9.05 am}. There is then a morning break an hour after the service at{ {10.30 am. At {12.00 pm }there is a dinner break, we finish dinner at about {12.30 pm} and have a playtime until{1.10 pm.} In the afternoon there is a break between{2.15 pm}and{2.30 pm.} We finish school at{3.10 pm.
